channel.title: Zamorak Platelegs
channel.description:
If you have seen my other topic, you will know by now im sort of completely the god armor sets (in my own way)
if you would like to see the zamorak chestplate, go here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,428708.0.html
if you have already seen it, just continue reading :)
After working on the chestplate and animating it, i knew that it would need some platelegs to go with it. here is what i have:
[b][size=16pt]Front View [IMG]http://i551.photobucket.com/albums/ii448/badger41badger41/zammylegs.png[/img]
Side View[/size] [IMG]http://i551.photobucket.com/albums/ii448/badger41badger41/zammylegs2.png[/img]
I hope you like them, as just like the chestplate, i plan on animating and releasing the legs as well.
